 href="https://www.deliciouslyella.com/en-eu/recipes/creamy-kale-and-sweet-potato-salad/"/><link rel="alternate" hrefLang="en-SM" href="https://www.deliciouslyella.com/en-eu/recipes/creamy-kale-and-sweet-potato-salad/"/><link rel="alternate" hrefLang="en-TR" href="https://www.deliciouslyella.com/en-eu/recipes/creamy-kale-and-sweet-potato-salad/"/><link rel="alternate" hrefLang="en-UA" href="https://www.deliciouslyella.com/en-eu/recipes/creamy-kale-and-sweet-potato-salad/"/><link rel="alternate" hrefLang="en-US" href="https://www.deliciouslyella.com/en-us/recipes/creamy-kale-and-sweet-potato-salad/"/><link rel="alternate" hrefLang="en-VA" href="https://www.deliciouslyella.com/en-eu/recipes/creamy-kale-and-sweet-potato-salad/"/><link rel="alternate" hrefLang="en-XK" href="https://www.deliciouslyella.com/en-eu/recipes/creamy-kale-and-sweet-potato-salad/"/><link rel="alternate" hrefLang="x-default" href="https://www.deliciouslyella.com/recipes/creamy-kale-and-sweet-potato-salad/"/><link rel="canonical" href="https://www.deliciouslyella.com/recipes/creamy-kale-and-sweet-potato-salad/"/><meta name="description" content="For this creamy kale &amp; sweet potato salad, chickpeas and sweet potatoes are roasted with paprika and cumin, then tossed through kale with a creamy cashew dressing and finished with a sprinkling of parsley, chilli flakes and black pepper."/><meta property="og:image:url" content="https://images.ctfassets.net/8ffyq0lxv9d2/3N5caHD03AfEq8k7Me0DYF/27a5316c0466144f918e5e0fc534c93c/kale_salad.jpg"/><meta property="og:image:height" content="7996"/><meta property="og:image:secure_url" content="https://images.ctfassets.net/8ffyq0lxv9d2/3N5caHD03AfEq8k7Me0DYF/27a5316c0466144f918e5e0fc534c93c/kale_salad.jpg"/><meta property="og:image:type" content="image/jpeg"/><meta property="og:image:width" content="5333"/><meta property="og:description" content="For this creamy kale &amp; sweet potato salad, chickpeas and sweet potatoes are roasted with paprika and cumin, then tossed through kale with a creamy cashew dressing and finished with a sprinkling of parsley, chilli flakes and black pepper."/><meta property="og:title" content="Creamy Kale &amp; Sweet Potato Salad | Deliciously Ella (UK)"/><meta property="og:url" content="https://www.deliciouslyella.com/recipes/creamy-kale-and-sweet-potato-salad/"/><meta name="twitter:description" content="For this creamy kale &amp; sweet potato salad, chickpeas and sweet potatoes are roasted with paprika and cumin, then tossed through kale with a creamy cashew dressing and finished with a sprinkling of parsley, chilli flakes and black pepper."/><meta name="twitter:title" content="Creamy Kale &amp; Sweet Potato Salad | Deliciously Ella (UK)"/><script type="application/ld+json">{"@context":"https://schema.org","@id":"https://deliciouslyella.com/recipes/creamy-kale-and-sweet-potato-salad","@type":"Recipe","author":{"@type":"Organization","name":"Deliciously Ella"},"recipeCategory":"Mains","url":"https://deliciouslyella.com/recipes/creamy-kale-and-sweet-potato-salad","name":"Creamy Kale & Sweet Potato Salad","image":"//images.ctfassets.net/8ffyq0lxv9d2/3N5caHD03AfEq8k7Me0DYF/27a5316c0466144f918e5e0fc534c93c/kale_salad.jpg","recipeIngredient":["2 sweet potatoes","8.5 oz canned chickpeas","1 teaspoon ground cumin","1 teaspoon paprika","7 oz kale","handful of parsley","pinch of dried red chilli flakes","drizzle of olive oil","pinch of sea salt & black pepper"],"cookTime":"PT35M","prepTime":"PTundefinedM","totalTime":"PT35M","recipeInstructions":[{"@type":"HowToStep","text":"Preheat oven to 190°C fan / 375°F. Place the sweet potato chunks and drained chickpeas on a baking tray and drizzle with olive oil, cumin, paprika and a pinch of salt. Mix well and roast for 30–35 minutes until the sweet potatoes begin to soften."},{"@type":"HowToStep","text":"While they cook, make the dressing. Place all of the dressing ingredients into a powerful blender and blitz until smooth."},{"@type":"HowToStep","text":"Place the kale into a large mixing bowl; add a drizzle of olive oil and a sprinkling of salt. Massage the kale with your hands for a few minutes, really rubbing the leaves until the kale is nice and soft. When ready, pour over the dressing and gently rub it into the kale, again using your hands."},{"@type":"HowToStep","text":"Once the sweet potatoes and chickpeas are cooked, remove from the oven. Allow to cool for a few minutes and then toss through the kale. Transfer to a serving bowl and finish with fresh parsley, a crack of black pepper and a pinch of chilli flakes."}],"recipeYield":4,"description":"Sweet potatoes and chickpeas are roasted with paprika and cumin, then tossed through kale with a creamy cashew dressing and finished with a sprinkling of parsley, chilli flakes and black pepper — simple, creamy and delicious.","datePublished":"7 January 2020"}</script><meta property="og:type" content="website"/><script>
