KS</a></label><label class="subtitle recipe-links-headline-item"><a class="" href="/collection/recipes/smoothies-&amp;-juices/">SMOOTHIES &amp; JUICES</a></label></div><div class="empty-block " style="height:30px"></div><div class="panel-hrList panel-hrList_1C "><div class="panel-hrList-headline"><div class=""><h3 class="panel-hrList-headline-title">Love this? Try these...</h3></div><div class="panel-hrList-headline-navButtons"><button class="styled-icon-button styled-icon-button_none " disabled=""><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="" fill="currentColor" font-size="1.5em" width="1em" height="1em"><path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M6.07851 10.6168C5.97451 10.6168 5.92251 10.4915 5.99051 10.4141C8.15984 7.93546 9.88384 5.97546 11.5932 4.00212C11.9332 3.61012 12.5398 3.20346 11.9732 2.61279C11.4105 2.02612 10.9705 2.58079 10.5732 2.93146C7.72384 5.44479 4.90651 7.99412 2.03317 10.4795C0.850507 11.5021 1.10651 12.2555 2.16251 13.1675C4.91584 15.5488 7.60517 18.0021 10.3452 20.3981C10.7625 20.7635 11.2918 21.5688 11.8612 21.0648C12.7505 20.2795 11.8052 19.8115 11.4158 19.3421C9.80117 17.3981 8.13851 15.4941 6.18517 13.2221C6.09184 13.1141 6.16784 12.9421 6.31184 12.9421C7.44117 12.9421 8.13584 12.9421 8.83051 12.9421C12.6318 12.9421 16.4332 12.9501 20.2358 12.9341C21.0545 12.9301 22.0532 13.2035 22.0132 11.7541C21.9732 10.3168 20.9625 10.6648 20.1558 10.6235L6.07851 10.6168Z"></path></svg></button><button class="styled-icon-button styled-icon-button_none "><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="" fill="currentColor" font-size="1.5em" width="1em" height="1em"><path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M17.188 12.9654C17.292 12.9654 17.344 13.0907 17.276 13.168C15.1067 15.6467 13.3827 17.6067 11.6733 19.58C11.3333 19.972 10.7267 20.3787 11.2933 20.9694C11.856 21.556 12.296 21.0014 12.6933 20.6507C15.5427 18.1374 18.36 15.588 21.2333 13.1027C22.416 12.08 22.16 11.3267 21.104 10.4147C18.3507 8.03336 15.6613 5.58003 12.9213 3.18403C12.504 2.81869 11.9747 2.01336 11