ies: omit the scattering of extra pine nuts for little ones."},"relatedRecipes":{"en-US":[{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"7mcNQYlMV9izCIgDu64KVb"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"5zMY9VaC8AAVR3VKpNr8MN"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"6YgBCKEQL9CkU0Ggb6beLe"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"1S4fDC8MFnsN6qhZ4QKMQC"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"1OLAI7feX6Ig0Vfybr5KVZ"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"5MIPRHrAYgQv4H7TiWc0OY"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"7wi1yH05TJZP6BsjJMkl4s"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"7mcNQYlMV9izCIgDu64KVb"}}]},"subcategories":{"en-US":[{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"3qZLSssZDvfTTFzVUBLkzb"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"6iEbcYjXGaIGM4T9c4e3CQ"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"2I2ItwDXUGl9AW1hy0fVVu"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"6YnDYQy5W8YqerUtYMsIrB"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"7iPp0sF3EPA26IttZ67dWA"}}]},"freezable":{"en-US":false},"nutrients":{"en-US":["1 of your 5 a day","Simple ingredients"]}},"contentType":"recipe","isAvailable":true,"new":false,"id":"73ju6qzxe1mbA6GJUBQhOe","contentfulType":"recipe","visibility":"Unlisted","presenter":{},"terms":{"en-US":"10 minute pea pesto orzo","de":""},"languages":["en-US"],"pillars":[],"isSleep":false,"isWater":false,"categories":["4S9ysV0FCbpKzx2VudQUAJ","2nNyXpAp40mosMAoI6iaiK","78ViO8imwz3dNO4mG1NtH"],"recipeCategories":[{"id":"4S9ysV0FCbpKzx2VudQUAJ","name":"Book Recipes"},{"id":"2nNyXpAp40mosMAoI6iaiK","name":"Mains"},{"id":"78ViO8imwz3dNO4mG1NtH","name":"Kids"}],"relatedTerms":{"en-US":"          sea salt black pepper  cannellini butter beans  extra virgin olive oil  clove garlic cloves  basil  pine nuts  frozen peas  orzo other short pasta  nutritional yeast ","de":""},"isPlantBased":false,"allergyIDs":["20t5UqLrQx1IV8uT4uwd2T","6ZMKWrKQhUpBOHASExzcQK"],"allergies":["Gluten","Nut"]},"1":{"metadata":{"tags":[{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Tag","id":"italian"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Tag","id":"pastas"}}]},"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"8ffyq0lxv9d2"}},"id":"7mcNQYlMV9izCIgDu64KVb","type":"Entry","createdAt":"2021-02-24T14:37:43.421Z","updatedAt":"2023-10-17T09:58:28.929Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"master","type":"Link","linkType":"Environment"}},"revision":28,"contentType":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"ContentType","id":"recipe"}}},"fields":{"title":{"de":"Cremige Orzo-Nudeln mit Pilzen","en-US":"Creamy Mushroom Orzo"},"slug":{"en-US":"creamy-mushroom-orzo"},"metaDescription":{"en-US":"A little like risotto but much quicker to make, orzo makes a delicious, quick dinner. The dried porcini mushrooms add depth and richness to this creamy mushroom orzo, while the coconut milk makes it wonderfully creamy."},"availableFrom":{"en-US":"2021-03-09T00:00"},"featuredFrom":{"en-US":"2023-11-28T00:00"},"featuredTo":{"en-US":"2022-11-29T00:00"},"featuredOrder":{"en-US":1},"categories":{"en-US":[{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"2nNyXpAp40mosMAoI6iaiK"}}]},"description":{"de":"Dieser Orzo ist einem Risotto ähnlich, nur ist er viel schneller gemacht. Deshalb eignet er sich ausgezeichnet als schnelles und leckeres Abendessen. Die getrockneten Steinpilze geben dem Gericht geschmackliche Tiefe und die Kokosmilch macht es richtig cremig. Die Pfanne einfache in der Mitte des Tisches stellen und mit einem einfachen grünen Salat und viel schwarzem Pfeffer servieren. ","en-US":"A little like risotto but much quicker to make, orzo makes a delicious, quick dinner. The dried porcini mushrooms add depth and richness, while the coconut milk makes it wonderfully creamy. Serve it in the centre of the table with a simple green salad and plenty of black pepper.","en-US-POSIX":"A little like risotto but much quicker to make, orzo makes a delicious, quick dinner. The dried porcini mushrooms add depth and richness, while the coconut milk makes it wonderfully creamy. Serve it in the center of the table with a simple green salad and plenty of black pepper."},"heroImage":{"en-US":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Asset","id":"4YmH7o1aUEHNgxx83DRFaQ"}}},"images":{"en-US":[{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Asset","id":"1jZKWY3EVYe31rVehAEpZT"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Asset","id":"Kae0ajgnKQhEBzefrSVsf"}}]},"servesMaximum":{"en-US":4},"totalMinutes":{"de":40,"en-US":40},"ingredientSections":{"en-US":[{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"720d0BqPQKRVvs86wKDV1z"}}]},"method":{"en-US":[{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"4CgumPUMHWc3mishcx5kVw"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"2RWhLZ4WBGWKH3owCaVelQ"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"5DqAtDr01e8qfFTtMCkWtg"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"3j2qn0FuobW6oKUZK5xCvO"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"3gDxojsYCG7LVYu0icUE0z"}}]},"relatedRecipes":{"en-US":[{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"ZAjJJQMhuHchKbulE2DIp"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"5paggqmQHo9ky6UazvYR20"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"3RRKrpiHH52IxgijG8mapE"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"01Ap4qEp01jFcT7mJmlmeh"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"6HPVulCO6VLqeaSHGiHXGh"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"498LsiaQHDaARbnRjvfWIk"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"56uyx6mSHQsyBOfly5wJMY"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"2NQ9XXjlgfuQ0pnBT55bbG"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"e8NmVvE7o3hv543fip14b"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"3I7u34IGE27T0SlkzTBsN3"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"3xloTtL5iz8gGrUBq9ACS1"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"2vqddoGTeGhDU0HifTMpqw"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"4XYlt6vtgtjendO2S7GvtJ"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"6sZ9