":"2025-12-23T14:01:48.888Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"master","type":"Link","linkType":"Environment"}},"publishedVersion":240,"revision":43,"contentType":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"ContentType","id":"recipe"}}},"fields":{"title":{"de":"Orzo-Nudeln mit gerösteter roter Paprika","en-US":"Roasted Red Pepper Orzo","en-US-POSIX":"Roasted Red Bell Pepper Orzo"},"slug":{"en-US":"roasted-red-pepper-orzo"},"metaDescription":{"en-US":"When it comes to easy comfort food for busy days, this roasted red pepper pasta dish is a weeknight winner — the sweet roasted peppers combined with soft orzo, make it supremely satisfying, plus it's packed full of flavour."},"availableFrom":{"en-US":"2021-05-14T00:00"},"featuredFrom":{"en-US":"2025-12-31T00:00"},"featuredTo":{"en-US":"2026-01-01T00:00"},"featuredOrder":{"en-US":1},"popularFrom":{"en-US":"2024-09-16T00:00"},"popularTo":{"en-US":"2024-09-23T00:00"},"popularOrder":{"en-US":19},"categories":{"en-US":[{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"2nNyXpAp40mosMAoI6iaiK"}}]},"description":{"de":"Wenn du dich an stressigen Tagen nach einfachem Comfort Food sehnst, sind diese Orzo-Nudeln die beste Wahl für ein Abendessen unter der Woche. Die gerösteten Paprika vermischt mit den weichen Orzo-Nudeln sind nicht nur sättigend, sondern bieten auch richtig viel Geschmack. Wenn ihr keine Orzo-Nudeln habt, verwendet stattdessen einfach Risotto-Reis oder Graupen.","en-US":"When it comes to easy comfort food for busy days, this pasta dish is a weeknight winner — the sweet roasted peppers combined with soft orzo, make it supremely satisfying, plus it's packed full of flavour. If you don't have orzo, simply swap for risotto rice or pearl barley.","en-US-POSIX":"When it comes to easy comfort food for busy days, this pasta dish is a weeknight winner — the sweet roasted bell peppers combined with soft orzo, make it supremely satisfying, plus it's packed full of flavor. If you don't have orzo, simply swap for risotto rice or pearl barley."}