I like to double the ragu quantities and keep the the leftovers to use across the week."},"availableFrom":{"en-US":"2021-09-28T00:00"},"featuredFrom":{"en-US":"2025-04-02T00:00"},"featuredTo":{"en-US":"2025-04-03T00:00"},"featuredOrder":{"en-US":1},"categories":{"en-US":[{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"2nNyXpAp40mosMAoI6iaiK"}}]},"description":{"de":"Ihr sucht nach einem echten Hingucker auf eurer Tafel für ein Abendessen mit Freunden oder für einen romantischen Abend zu Hause? Hier kommt das Rezept für euch! Es sieht toll aus, steckt voller Geschmack, und die Brösel machen es schön knusprig. Ich mache immer gleich doppelt so viel Tomatenragout und genieße es während der Woche. Es schmeckt perfekt zu Nudeln.","en-US":"This show-stopping centre piece is full of delicious flavours and textures. I often make a double batch of the ragu and use the rest throughout the week — it makes a fantastic speedy pasta sauce.  ","en-US-POSIX":"This show-stopping centre piece is full of flavor and textures — the breadcrumbs give it a perfect little crunch on top. I like to double the ragu quantities and keep the the leftovers to use across the week; it makes a perfect, speedy pasta sauce.  "},"heroImage":{"en-US":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Asset","id":"76nXaGNBf3sc0Bqja7nW7n"}}},"images":{"en-US":[{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Asset","id":"6GSZkKV51NnRFSzeuB5vK"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Asset","id":"4NzEcvVmVg3pSUGtJ2V0Jb"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Asset","id":"5sJxMIFjsTaJXwSz1tXMuo"}}]},"servesMaximum":{"en-US":4},"totalMinutes":{"en-US":45},"ingredientSections":{"en-US":[{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"R2LIWHgzudAvV0qkjDVuo"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"15VpyseCiVII8sbs708NJp"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"7LkznfDglhwBGJJ1cqWSLE"}}]},"method":{"en-US":[{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"mXItOyA12Bg6kxprYXnxu"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"JOu9esszfgO