d healthy fats. Including apple and cinnamon may also help to support healthy digestion."},"availableFrom":{"en-US":"2022-10-18T00:00"},"featuredFrom":{"en-US":"2025-10-13T00:00"},"featuredTo":{"en-US":"2025-10-14T00:00"},"featuredOrder":{"en-US":1},"popularFrom":{"en-US":"2023-01-19T00:00"},"popularTo":{"en-US":"2023-02-08T00:00"},"visibility":{"en-US":"All Access"},"categories":{"en-US":[{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"2IpnFlvZu0qAy4wK0eye00"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"78ViO8imwz3dNO4mG1NtH"}}]},"description":{"de":"Starte deinen Tag richtig und zwar mit einer wärmenden Schüssel voller Porridge. Das leckere Frühstück ist mit Hanfsamen und Chiasamen ausgestattet und versorgt dich bereits am Morgen mit Ballaststoffen, Proteinen und gesunden Fetten. Die Geschmacksrichtung aus Apfel und Zimt schmeckt nicht nur köstlich, sondern unterstützt auch die gesunde Verdauung und reduziert Entzündungen. ","en-US":"Start your day right with a warming bowl of creamy porridge — with hemp and chia seeds, it’s supercharged with fibre, protein and healthy fats. Including apple and cinnamon may also help to support healthy digestion and reduce inflammation. ","en-US-POSIX":"Start your day right with a warming bowl of creamy porridge — with hemp and chia seeds, it’s supercharged with fiber, protein and healthy fats. Including apple and cinnamon may also help to support healthy digestion and reduce inflammation. "},"heroImage":{"en-US":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Asset","id":"6lIRCYzxf2cuTkbBEaUmJP"}}},"servesMaximum":{"en-US":1},"cookTimeText":{"de":"Minuten"},"totalMinutes":{"en-US":10},"ingredientSections":{"en-US":[{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"6g71hoyPQCtaWag9PhoAq9"}}]},"method":{"en-US":[{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"0j4uYNgxBEnOq5okOnyn6"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"3BUq9Zi7WXS2Zi76lkQBuo"}}]},"relatedRecipes":{"en-US":[{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"1TJmRRzJPu8Yu8uM