ink","linkType":"Entry","id":"2IpnFlvZu0qAy4wK0eye00"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"78ViO8imwz3dNO4mG1NtH"}}]},"description":{"de":"Dieses Schoko-Porridge ist in ein paar Minuten fertig und das perfekte Frühstück für jeden Tag in der Woche. Der Kakao gibt ihm einen köstlich schokoladigen Geschmack, das Ahornsirup sorgt für etwas Süße. Wir rühren gerne noch große saftige Rosinen unter und servieren es mit frischen Himbeeren, Mandelmus und Kokos-Chips.","en-US":"These quick chocolate oats take just a few minutes to pull together and make the perfect breakfast for any day of the week. The cacao adds a delicious chocolate taste, while the maple syrup adds a hint of sweetness. We love to mix through big juicy raisins and serve with some fresh raspberries, almond butter and coconut chips on top.","en-US-POSIX":"This chocolate oatmeal takes just a few minutes to pull together and makes the perfect breakfast for any day of the week. The cacao adds a delicious chocolate taste while the maple syrup adds a hint of sweetness. We love to mix through big juicy raisins and serve with some fresh raspberries, almond butter and coconut chips on top."},"heroImage":{"en-US":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Asset","id":"6aRF2parPgpqQXJ6zEjtP6"}}},"images":{"en-US":[{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Asset","id":"4Hl6Sud8PFJyJYx9tM9PFS"}}]},"servesMinimum":{"en-US":2},"servesMaximum":{"en-US":2},"totalMinutes":{"en-US":5},"ingredientSections":{"en-US":[{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"50hDOrkFCxrZhdhNY2FQjq"}}]},"method":{"en-US":[{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"TPAlXixiViONBk0M6Cnxk"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"HmzjolhbgaQj2lOKEUqXj"}}]},"relatedRecipes":{"en-US":[{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"5IYgFrwki2VsM5L6l13gy7"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"73ezxZSMPefxUPab9V92GL"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"3uCZoZmBGzhAtvg8Cf7lzE"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry"