,"linkType":"Space","id":"8ffyq0lxv9d2"}},"id":"2L5TnwfbIZyOuZkX2TFuMs","type":"Entry","createdAt":"2021-01-11T14:22:46.806Z","updatedAt":"2025-09-05T11:06:15.617Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"master","type":"Link","linkType":"Environment"}},"publishedVersion":89,"revision":14,"contentType":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"ContentType","id":"recipe"}}},"fields":{"title":{"de":"Porridge mit Apfel \u0026 Zimt","en-US":"Apple \u0026 Cinnamon Porridge","en-US-POSIX":"Apple \u0026 Cinnamon Oatmeal"},"slug":{"en-US":"apple-and-cinnamon-porridge"},"metaDescription":{"en-US":"This apple \u0026 cinnamon porridge is the ultimate breakfast on a cold winter day. The cinnamon and apple taste delicious mixed through the creamy oats, with some coconut sugar adding a little sweetness to the whole thing. "},"availableFrom":{"en-US":"2021-03-03T00:00"},"featuredFrom":{"en-US":"2025-09-12T00:00"},"featuredTo":{"en-US":"2025-09-13T00:00"},"featuredOrder":{"en-US":1},"categories":{"en-US":[{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"2IpnFlvZu0qAy4wK0eye00"}}]},"description":{"de":"Dieses Porridge mit Apfel \u0026 Zimt ist das ultimative Frühstück an einem kalten Wintertag. Zimt und Apfel schmecken köstlich in den cremigen Haferflocken, der Kokosblütenzucker verleiht dem Porridge etwas Süße. Wir genießen es am liebsten mit einem Kompott aus gemischten Beeren, etwas Mandelmus und bestreut mit Granola.","en-US":"This apple \u0026 cinnamon porridge is the ultimate breakfast on a cold winter day. The cinnamon and apple taste delicious mixed through the creamy oats, with some coconut sugar adding a little sweetness to the whole thing. We love to serve this with mixed berry compote, some almond butter and a sprinkle of granola. ","en-US-POSIX":"This apple and cinnamon oatmeal is the ultimate breakfast on a cold winter day. The cinnamon and apple taste delicious mixed through the creamy oatmeal, with some coconut sugar adding a little sweetness to the whole thing. We love to serve this with