ato gnocchi is surprisingly easy to make. Served with pan-fried, garlicky mushrooms and fresh thyme, we like to finish it off with a drizzle of pesto."},"heroImage":{"en-US":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Asset","id":"4lut6NsMZi7LgbT5qtwA3C"}}},"images":{"en-US":[{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Asset","id":"6V5IMEqBdTyLIQQSZzqfj9"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Asset","id":"4MqaIAzIsTwEXKCWKpFYmI"}}]},"servesMinimum":{"en-US":2},"servesMaximum":{"en-US":2},"totalMinutes":{"en-US":45},"ingredientSections":{"en-US":[{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"6vF8D8pxdYmo9wjRETDoOf"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"60KQ0w5PwADKYhQIpZjhYt"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"2FUr8Kj9uSXiyq5RgAfacq"}}]},"method":{"en-US":[{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"3a8ADYu8x4OFMLKzC1udbU"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"5EPSyDQEZWFQvQjXuMShZh"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"7fVSbdsQA8Fn7Zejgj0JoQ"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"2p6jy7LupJolIydkbWAiOs"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"6zYFabrMqgBA6lkeHRPBma"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"3r5d8tUG05hXBzHh5lJ2fV"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"1o0JLa8AX0cm7v8kteOaFm"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"4mGtKnbUl88rJHZcjleYdn"}}]},"tip":{"de":"Für dieses Gericht benötigst du ein Weißmehl – du kannst glutenfreies oder normales weißes Mehl verwenden, aber ersetze es nicht durch Alternativen, wie Buchweizenmehl, Reismehl oder Kokosmehl.","en-US":"This dish does need plain flour — you can use gluten-free or regular plain flour, but don’t swap it for an alternative such as buckwheat, rice or coconut flour."},"relatedRecipes":{"en-US":[{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"528yKob488uKoQQES02GA8"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"lt3awtaqiK3rrtim7vSX1"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"1svupjeXcQimSyCKsuCaiS"}},{"sys":{"type":"Lin