IX":"Friends coming round for dinner? Wondering what to cook? The beauty of this Spinach \u0026 ‘Ricotta’ Stuffed Pasta Bake is that it looks great on the table, it’s creamy \u0026 indulgent, but it’s packed with healthy fiber \u0026 protein."},"availableFrom":{"en-US":"2023-11-13T00:00"},"featuredFrom":{"en-US":"2026-02-07T00:00"},"featuredTo":{"en-US":"2026-02-08T00:00"},"featuredOrder":{"en-US":1},"popularFrom":{"en-US":"2024-01-02T00:00"},"popularTo":{"en-US":"2024-01-08T00:00"},"popularOrder":{"en-US":13},"categories":{"en-US":[{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"2nNyXpAp40mosMAoI6iaiK"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"GIFhxoAcB9A7sBWJDAFoi"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"78ViO8imwz3dNO4mG1NtH"}}]},"description":{"de":"Es kommen Freunde zum Abendessen vorbei und du fragst dich, was du kochen sollst? Das Schöne an diesem Gericht ist, dass es sowohl richtig toll auf dem Tisch aussieht als auch cremig und unwiderstehlich lecker ist. Trotzdem ist es auch vollgepackt mit gesunden Ballaststoffen und Proteinen. Diese gefüllte Pasta aus dem Ofen kannst du auch gut vorbereiten, indem du die Tomatensoße am Tag davor zubereitest und die Füllung eine Stunde vor dem Backen machst. Einfach perfekt!","en-US":"Friends coming round for dinner? Wondering what to cook? The beauty of this dish is that it looks great on the table, it’s creamy \u0026 indulgent, but it’s packed with healthy fibre \u0026 protein. You can also prep ahead, by making the tomato sauce the day before and the pasta filling an hour before baking. Perfect!","en-US-POSIX":"Friends coming round for dinner? Wondering what to cook? The beauty of this dish is that it looks great on the table, it’s creamy \u0026 indulgent, but it’s packed with healthy fiber \u0026 protein. You can also prep ahead, by making the tomato sauce the day before and the pasta filling an hour before baking. Perfect!"},"heroImage":{"en-US":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Asset","id":"5tLFLUn0QT