"de":"Dieser Nudelauflauf ist perfekt, wenn ihr ein einfaches aber köstliches Gericht sucht. Die Nudeln und dünnen Zucchini-Scheiben werden von cremigem Pesto aus Cashews und Basilikum umhüllt. Zum Backen wird der Auflauf mit Brotkrumen bestreut.","en-US":"This pasta bake is a great recipe to make when you're looking for something simple and delicious. The pasta is coated with a creamy cashew and basil pesto, teamed with thinly sliced courgette and topped with a crunchy breadcrumb topping.","en-US-POSIX":"This pasta bake is a great recipe to make when you're looking for something simple and delicious. The pasta is coated with a creamy cashew and basil pesto, teamed with thinly sliced zucchini and topped with a crunchy breadcrumb topping."},"heroImage":{"en-US":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Asset","id":"3hBZfg81PKAUW9Lnc6WHUD"}}},"images":{"en-US":[{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Asset","id":"15vetGWmZeJMVnP39Ef32A"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Asset","id":"7ok88IIEze9AQNwwHItNmJ"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Asset","id":"iEbySpIA5Qbxc3Jo4gsTG"}}]},"servesMaximum":{"en-US":4},"totalMinutes":{"en-US":30},"ingredientSections":{"en-US":[{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"3Sm9wMqosvPGgNa1iKW7DN"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"3KeNiyyhT24eINQx89ZNFI"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"5VxPcUO5MdumRmNfk4uj6t"}}]},"method":{"en-US":[{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"3F35F04rwPmN9Nhq04gY2y"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"4u1mozhEL0jezYLX3DQEpA"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"1TGmw8fbph7fevmfS73Kqu"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"6TyMG6fkOBz86DeroDAYBm"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"4dTTGgyu2vJvS1xILaWK24"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"2to5aDOwLQFvDas83GhmCb"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"4rC4QmU0cwISXd8jGphfWu"}}]},"subcategories":{"en-US":[{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"6iE