gano, balsamic and garlic, then tossed through pasta, topped with vegan white sauce and finished with a lovely layer of breadcrumbs."},"availableFrom":{"en-US":"2021-03-02T00:00"},"featuredFrom":{"en-US":"2025-11-07T00:00"},"featuredTo":{"en-US":"2025-11-08T00:00"},"featuredOrder":{"en-US":1},"categories":{"en-US":[{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"2nNyXpAp40mosMAoI6iaiK"}}]},"description":{"de":"In diesem Gericht treffen Nudeln mit Tomatensoße auf Käse-Makkaroni. Sonnengetrocknete Tomaten werden mit Oregano, Balsamico und Knoblauch geköchelt, dann mit den Nudeln vermischt und mit einer veganen weißen Soße und einer Schicht knuspriger Brotbrösel überbacken – eine wunderbare Kombination. Bei diesem einfachen Gericht für Abende unter der Woche handelt es sich um ultimatives Comfort Food.","en-US":"Tomato pasta meets mac and cheese? Yes please. Sun-dried tomatoes are simmered with oregano, balsamic and garlic, then tossed through pasta, topped with vegan white sauce and finished with a lovely layer of crispy breadcrumbs — a winning combination. This easy weeknight supper is the ultimate comfort food."},"heroImage":{"en-US":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Asset","id":"6ncvbuH2JxZV9PO28fMOMv"}}},"images":{"en-US":[{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Asset","id":"nOtqNnQ3xhLX01s1OQSHY"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Asset","id":"4ItpA1qwvaRW9LNma8Sdb7"}}]},"servesMaximum":{"en-US":4},"totalMinutes":{"en-US":35},"ingredientSections":{"en-US":[{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"4v7o4rMYbYPVV79H2A1Z7A"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"7ylc1KvX0F5BYebgAvTbHR"}}]},"method":{"en-US":[{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"4GLh9lZFLEqM7es47V7uuJ"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"3xc7fodZC8KRDScoOKveIt"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"55ApAAUUoChT2zSI1CkGqp"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"38ab5hlqY0D9dya6KqW32p"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"2lxSYslYMP4moIlz