00:00"},"featuredFrom":{"en-US":"2021-12-04T00:00"},"featuredTo":{"en-US":"2021-12-05T00:00"},"featuredOrder":{"en-US":1},"categories":{"en-US":[{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"2nNyXpAp40mosMAoI6iaiK"}}]},"description":{"de":"Diese Linsensuppe mit Kurkuma gehört zu den besten Wohlfühl-Suppen aller Zeiten. Die Linsen, Möhren und Mandelmilch zusammen machen sie schön cremig und Kurkuma, Knoblauch, Senfsamen und Kreuzkümmel sorgen für einen vollen, vielfältigen Geschmack. Jeder Löffel ist wunderbar. Ich serviere sie gerne mit gerösteten, knackigen Kräuter-Cashews, weil sie noch mehr Aromen und Textur in die Suppe bringen. ","en-US":"This turmeric and lentil soup is just amazing, it’s the most comforting soup. The lentils, carrots and almond milk together make it thick and creamy, while the turmeric, garlic, mustard seeds and cumin give it such a deep, rich flavour so every spoonful really bursts with goodness. We love serving it topped with roasted herby cashews, as these make it even more flavoursome, plus they add texture to the smooth soup with a nice added crunch. ","en-US-POSIX":"This turmeric and lentil soup is just amazing, it’s the most comforting soup ever. The lentils, carrots and almond milk together make it so thick and creamy, while the turmeric, garlic, mustard seeds and cumin give it such a deep, rich flavor so every spoonful really bursts with delicious goodness. I love serving it topped with roasted herby cashews, as these make it even more flavorsome, plus they add texture to the smooth soup with a nice added crunch."},"heroImage":{"en-US":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Asset","id":"6L4AyTYDRLfCVKQL94UfMI"}}},"images":{"en-US":[{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Asset","id":"2jlzOmlfzwROYnIUybnMa8"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Asset","id":"5Xi4F3MzUWjHNAZbzl1wia"}}]},"servesMinimum":{"en-US":2},"servesMaximum":{"en-US":2},"prepTimeText":{"de":"60 Minuten","en-US":"60 minutes"},"cookTimeText":{"de":"35 Minuten","en-US":"35 minut