inkType":"Environment"}},"publishedVersion":168,"revision":16,"contentType":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"ContentType","id":"recipe"}}},"fields":{"title":{"de":"Cremiges Süßkartoffel-Dip","en-US":"Creamy Sweet Potato Dip"},"slug":{"en-US":"creamy-sweet-potato-dip"},"metaDescription":{"en-US":"Sweet potato is one of my favourite vegetables, and it works so well when blended into a creamy sweet potato dip. The miso paste adds incredible flavour here, while the almond butter creates delicious texture."},"availableFrom":{"en-US":"2019-01-17T00:00"},"featuredOrder":{"en-US":1},"popularFrom":{"en-US":"2020-01-17T00:00"},"popularTo":{"en-US":"2020-01-31T00:00"},"popularOrder":{"en-US":6},"categories":{"en-US":[{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"6E04w6vzcQwcswKIsIKeEI"}}]},"description":{"de":"Süßkartoffeln gehören zu meinen Lieblingsgemüsesorten und sie sind perfekt für einen cremigen Dip. In dieser Version sorgt die Miso-Paste für eine unglaubliche Geschmacksnote und das Mandelmus macht das Dip noch cremiger. Wir essen es immer gleich auf, am liebsten mit Karotten, Fladenbrot oder frisch getoastetem Sauerteigbrot.","en-US":"Sweet potato is one of my favourite vegetables, and it works so well when blended into a creamy dip. The miso paste adds incredible flavour here, while the almond butter creates delicious texture. We love to eat ours as soon as it is made, served with carrots, pitta bread or freshly toasted sourdough. ","en-US-POSIX":"Sweet potato is one of my favorite vegetables and it works so well when blended into a creamy dip. The miso paste adds incredible flavor here, while the almond butter creates a delicious texture. We love to eat ours as soon as it is made, served with carrots, pita bread or freshly toasted sourdough. "},"heroImage":{"en-US":{"metadata":{"tags":[]},"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"8ffyq0lxv9d2"}},"id":"22QtrA0wxayCM5RtxXdBsH","type":"Asset","createdAt":"2019-01-29T16:36:40.749Z","updatedAt":"2019