vailable":true,"new":false,"id":"4f2q3SoZzdMp8E0MyligzY","contentfulType":"recipe","visibility":"Public","featured":false,"featuredOrder":1,"presenter":{},"terms":{"en-US":"hasselback sweet potatoes","de":"hasselback susskartoffeln"},"languages":["de","en-US","en-US-POSIX"],"pillars":[],"isSleep":false,"isWater":false,"categories":["2nNyXpAp40mosMAoI6iaiK"],"recipeCategories":[{"id":"2nNyXpAp40mosMAoI6iaiK","name":"Mains"}],"relatedTerms":{"en-US":"       olive oil  sweet potato potatoes  maple syrup  ground cinnamon  paprika  sea salt ","de":""},"isPlantBased":false,"allergyIDs":[],"allergies":[]},"8":{"metadata":{"tags":[],"concepts":[]},"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"8ffyq0lxv9d2"}},"id":"2FwqbwLic8YCYIGOSIkUke","type":"Entry","createdAt":"2018-12-20T08:33:59.119Z","updatedAt":"2024-01-04T17:50:59.694Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"development","type":"Link","linkType":"Environment"}},"publishedVersion":152,"revision":29,"contentType":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"ContentType","id":"recipe"}}},"fields":{"title":{"de":"Grünkohlsalat mit Granatapfel \u0026 Avocado","en-US":"Kale, Pomegranate \u0026 Avocado Salad"},"slug":{"en-US":"kale-pomegranate-and-avocado-salad"},"metaDescription":{"en-US":"We’ve kept this kale salad simple and just added avocado, pumpkin seeds and pomegranates, but it’s delicious with just about anything!"},"availableFrom":{"en-US":"2019-02-06T00:00"},"featuredFrom":{"en-US":"2019-05-14T00:00"},"featuredTo":{"en-US":"2019-05-15T00:00"},"featuredOrder":{"en-US":1},"quickEasyFrom":{"en-US":"2019-03-14T00:00"},"quickEasyTo":{"en-US":"2019-05-17T00:00"},"quickEasyOrder":{"en-US":2},"categories":{"en-US":[{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"2nNyXpAp40mosMAoI6iaiK"}}]},"description":{"de":"Meine Mutter und ich machen diesen Salat seit Jahren und wir sind noch immer total begeistert. Auch wenn es seltsam klingt, den Grünkkohl zu massieren, er wird dadurch schön weich. Das Dressing aus Tahini, Apfelweinessig und Limettensaft macht den Salat schön cremig. Diese Variante enthält nur Avocado, Kürbiskerne und Granatapfelkerne, aber er schmeckt mit fast allem. Ich mache ihn auch mit in Chili gebackenen Kichererbsen, gebackenen Süßkartoffeln, gedünstetem Gemüse, Kartoffeln aus dem Ofen, Roggen-Croutons und was ich sonst noch so in der Küche finde!","en-US":"My mum and I have been making this for years and we’re still completely obsessed. Massaging the kale may sound strange, but it works brilliantly to soften it, while the tahini, cider vinegar and lime dressing makes it so creamy. We’ve kept it simple here and just added avocado, pumpkin seeds and pomegranates, but it’s delicious with just about anything - I add roasted chilli chickpeas, baked sweet potatoes, sautéed veggies, roast potatoes, rye croutons and anything else I’ve got in my kitchen! ","en-US-POSIX":"My mum and I have been making this for years and we’re still completely obsessed. Massaging the kale may sound strange, but it works brilliantly to soften it, whilst the tahini, cider vinegar and lime dressing makes it so creamy. We’ve kept it simple here and just added avocado, pepitas and pomegranates, but it’s delicious with just about anything- I add roasted chili garbanzos, baked sweet potatoes, sautéed veggies, roast potatoes, rye croutons and anything else I’ve got in my kitchen!"},"heroImage":{"en-US":{"metadata":{"tags":[],"concepts":[]},"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"8ffyq0lxv9d2"}},"id":"6WHAsNWdxKa4usG6Yk26Gi","type":"Asset","createdAt":"2018-12-20T08:32:34.324Z","updatedAt":"2024-11-21T15:51:17.254Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"master","type":"Link","linkType":"Environment"}},"publishedVersion":21,"revision":2},"fields":{"title":{"en-US":"Kale Avo Pomegranate Salad"},"file":{"en-US":{"url":"//images.ctfassets.net/8ffyq0lxv9d2/6WHAsNWdxKa4usG6Yk26Gi/d42fad3cb4b9111a88cae0abed82f400/18-05-14-KaleAvoPomegranateSalad-2__1_.jpg","details":{"size":2260210,"image":{"width":3587,"height":5381}},"fileName":"18-05-14-KaleAvoPomegranateSalad-2 (1).jpg","contentType":"image/jpeg"}}},"id":"6WHAsNWdxKa4usG6Yk26Gi"}},"images":{"en-US":[{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Asset","id":"2V6OrdnnTGwCWgmOiuE6wM"}}]},"servesMaximum":{"en-US":2},"prepTimeText":{"de":"10 Minuten","en-US":"10 minutes"},"totalMinutes":{"en-US":10},"ingredientSections":{"en-US":[{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"4TPeNBcio8ukieCwC0YogS"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"COnnanSFBAkAWgqiSuSqc"}}]},"method":{"en-US":[{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"5OMc0NoS76YUo6QoIEmMq8"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"4my8k5MyRqcUkGq2KwEkam"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"1VYx4AR7VGm6G8we4KYYCO"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"56PtLyah3GIqAe4muEIIig"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"5ORqgXyntpRgA16ukjIR0V"}}]},"relatedRecipes":{"en-US":[{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"6bLN1U4heEs06csYaCu88S"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"3fu2E7dE9O8gUm6os2Qu26"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"4Kd4PT1L9D33E6v9Njtpp4"}}]},"subcategories":{"en-US":[{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"1lP0PIf0m3xvIQb3OoRT1K"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"6bfjhWWwJuymYWTg00eX17"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"1l7VOc1tKoJMiRD9I1ZwVv"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"5EPrj8oSzxJpVFNcpZrdPd"}}]},"freezable":{"en-US":false},"nutrients":{"en-US":["Source of fibre","Source of iron","Source of protein","Source of zinc","Source of calcium","Source of antioxidants"]}},"contentType":"recipe","isAvailable":true,"new":false,"id":"2FwqbwLic8YCYIGOSIkUke","contentfulType":"recipe","visibility":"Public","featured":false,"featuredOrder":1,"presenter":{},"terms":{"en-US":"kale pomegranate avocado salad","de":"grunkohlsalat mit granatapfel avocado"},"languages":["de","en-US","en-US-POSIX"],"pillars":[],"isSleep":false,"isWater":false,"categories":["2nNyXpAp40mosMAoI6iaiK"],"recipeCategories":[{"id":"2nNyXpAp40mosMAoI6iaiK","name":"Mains"}],"relatedTerms":{"en-US":"        olive oil  sea salt  tahini  lime limes  tamari  apple cider vinegar         pomegranate seeds  avocado avocados  kale  pumpkin seeds  garlic garlics  bread  extra virgin olive oil ","de":""},"isPlantBased":false,"allergyIDs":["20t5UqLrQx1IV8uT4uwd2T","6uCe4dc2c3PYrpksgs7uLK","1iGRpljRkbtERkTHItifoW"],"allergies":["Gluten","Sesame","Soya"]},"9":{"metadata":{"tags":[{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Tag","id":"american"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Tag","id":"cilantro"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Tag","id":"mexican"}}],"concepts":[]},"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"8ffyq0lxv9d2"}},"id":"7pEL0u2bodUkIR7gDcvOvS","type":"Entry","createdAt":"2020-06-08T15:37:25.251Z","updatedAt":"2025-01-20T14:34:13.970Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"master","type":"Link","linkType":"Environment"}},"publishedVersion":137,"revision":28,"contentType":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"ContentType","id":"recipe"}}},"fields":{"title":{"de":"Süßkartoffelpommes mit Tofu und Avocado","en-US":"Loaded Chilli Sweet Potato Fries","en-US-POSIX":"Loaded Chili Sweet Potato Fries"},"slug":{"en-US":"loaded-chilli-sweet-potato-fries"},"metaDescription":{"en-US":"This is the perfect dish to share with friends and family. The paprika roasted sweet potato fries taste delicious topped with crumbled tofu, piping hot chilli, creamy avocado smash and coconut yoghurt. "},"availableFrom":{"en-US":"2020-06-25T00:00"},"featuredFrom":{"en-US":"2020-07-26T00:00"},"featuredTo":{"en-US":"2020-07-27T00:00"},"featuredOrder":{"en-US":1},"categories":{"en-US":[{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"2nNyXpAp40mosMAoI6iaiK"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"699GpaVDhIHdkG5kFoUaP0"}}]},"description":{"de":"Ein perfektes Gericht für Freunde und Familie. Die mit Paprika gebackenen Süßkartoffelpommes schmecken mit zerkrümeltem Tofu, heißem, scharfem Chili, cremigem Avocadomus und Kokosjoghurt besonders lecker. Wir mögen sie am liebsten mit einem extra Spritzer Limettensaft, etwas frischer Chili für mehr Schärfe und einer Handvoll Koriander. ","en-US":"This is the perfect dish to share with friends and family. The paprika roasted sweet potato fries taste delicious topped with crumbled tofu, piping hot chilli, creamy avocado smash and coconut yoghurt. We love to squeeze even more lime juice on top, with some fresh red chilli for a kick of spice and a handful of coriander.","en-US-POSIX":"This is the perfect dish to share with friends and family. The paprika oven baked sweet potato fries taste delicious topped with crumbled tofu, piping hot chili, creamy avocado smash and coconut yogurt. We love to squeeze even more lime juice on top, with some fresh red chili for a kick of spice and a handful of cilantro."},"heroImage":{"en-US":{"metadata":{"tags":[]},"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"8ffyq0lxv9d2"}},"id":"6Dbk4ZbzmQIoaFbAJRCTJ4","type":"Asset","createdAt":"2020-06-08T15:20:51.427Z","updatedAt":"2020-06-08T15:20:51.427Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"master","type":"Link","linkType":"Environment"}},"revision":1},"fields":{"title":{"en-US":"19-012-04-LoadedChilliSweetPotatoFries-4"},"file":{"en-US":{"url":"//images.ctfassets.net/8ffyq0lxv9d2/6Dbk4ZbzmQIoaFbAJRCTJ4/784507aa92a0965bb20890ef4fafe844/19-012-04-LoadedChilliSweetPotatoFries-4.jpg","details":{"size":18641709,"image":{"width":3648,"height":5472}},"fileName":"19-012-04-LoadedChilliSweetPotatoFries-4.jpg","contentType":"image/jpeg"}}},"id":"6Dbk4ZbzmQIoaFbAJRCTJ4"}},"images":{"en-US":[{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Asset","id":"1PhcoF527klbUpsANbn6up"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Asset","id":"2d2xhdH0aakO2nYE58hLxL"}}]},"servesMaximum":{"en-US":4},"servesAlternateText":{"en-US":"4"},"totalMinutes":{"en-US":60},"ingredientSections":{"en-US":[{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"5FX3