:"2025-11-27T08:50:34.472Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"master","type":"Link","linkType":"Environment"}},"publishedVersion":137,"revision":24,"contentType":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"ContentType","id":"recipe"}}},"fields":{"title":{"de":"Süßkartoffelspalten mit Avocado-Salsa und Peperoni","en-US":"Loaded Sweet Potato Wedges"},"slug":{"en-US":"loaded-sweet-potato-wedges"},"metaDescription":{"en-US":"A great dinner or sharing snack for any day of the week, these sweet potato wedges are topped with heaps of homemade avocado salsa, crunchy red onions, spicy jalapeños and coriander."},"availableFrom":{"en-US":"2021-02-21T00:00"},"featuredFrom":{"en-US":"2025-12-05T00:00"},"featuredTo":{"en-US":"2025-12-06T00:00"},"featuredOrder":{"en-US":1},"popularFrom":{"en-US":"2025-02-01T00:00"},"popularTo":{"en-US":"2025-02-01T00:00"},"categories":{"en-US":[{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"2nNyXpAp40mosMAoI6iaiK"}}]},"description":{"de":"Diese Süßkartoffelspalten sind ein buntes, köstliches Gericht für jeden Abend in der Woche. Die Süßkartoffelspalten werden mit Olivenöl und Paprika gebacken, bis sie innen weich und außen knusprig sind. Dann belegen wir sie mit einer großen Ladung selbstgemachter Avocado-Salsa, knusprigen roten Zwiebeln, scharfer Peperoni und Koriander. Wir geben gerne noch ein paar Spritzer unserer liebsten scharfen Soße darüber. Aber sie schmecken auch ohne ganz köstlich.","en-US":"A great dinner or sharing snack for any day of the week, these sweet potato wedges are roasted in paprika and olive oil until they're soft on the inside and crispy on the outside. Finish them off topped with heaps of homemade avocado salsa, crunchy red onions, spicy jalapeños and coriander — we also love a drizzle of our favourite hot sauce over the top.","en-US-POSIX":"A great dinner or sharing snack for any day of the week, these sweet potato wedges are roasted in paprika and olive oil until they're soft on the inside and crispy on the outside. Finish them off topped with heaps of homemade avocado salsa, crunchy red onions, spicy jalapeños and cilantro — we also love a drizzle of our favourite hot sauce over the top."},"heroImage":{"en-US":{"metadata":{"tags":[]},"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"8ffyq0lxv9d2"}},"id":"37ej5ZY6M3cqzOIT4UIskZ","type":"Asset","createdAt":"2021-01-13T14:37:57.644Z","updatedAt":"2021-01-13T14:44:15.690Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"master","type":"Link","linkType":"Environment"}},"revision":2},"fields":{"title":{"en-US":"© Safia Shakarchi - Deliciously Ella - Sweet Potato Nachos - Re Edit -26"},"file":{"en-US":{"url":"//images.ctfassets.net/8ffyq0lxv9d2/37ej5ZY6M3cqzOIT4UIskZ/0fb7208db1370db6952010da09642113/___Safia_Shakarchi_-_Deliciously_Ella_-_Sweet_Potato_Nachos_-_Re_Edit_-26.jpg","details":{"size":2883253,"image":{"width":2302,"height":3068}},"fileName":"___Safia_Shakarchi_-_Deliciously_Ella_-_Sweet_Potato_Nachos_-_Re_Edit_-26.jpg","contentType":"image/jpeg"}}},"id":"37ej5ZY6M3cqzOIT4UIskZ"}},"images":{"en-US":[{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Asset","id":"oSDWxNRH64uBTid1yY6OR"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Asset","id":"2mzJzNE2pPhHQSFie5KUWW"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Asset","id":"25BBSh1FSydMUR5mNPBN4p"}}]},"servesMaximum":{"en-US":4},"totalMinutes":{"en-US":35},"ingredientSections":{"en-US":[{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"5Lm6gYMJOFrzjRTq4wq1zB"}}]},"method":{"en-US":[{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"1OCNyb6OgaDxWvq2GTDYQJ"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"34ABV5wMCSea43JxOmKz8X"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"5jGZvT6FTFNRLp2YZGr3ZB"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"4cSWPSc8qwmnSkZMzk94GS"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"7Kzn75pesn92x4UP1RVas8"}}]},"relatedRecipes":{"en-US":[{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"4maMk3JmnMJf0YA2oZwDrv"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"1UvfIlg1nPAMwFXC8BEFZ2"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkTy