"2018-12-13T00:00"},"categories":{"en-US":[{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"2nNyXpAp40mosMAoI6iaiK"}}]},"description":{"de":"Dieser Salat ist perfekt als sättigendes Mittagessen für jeden Tag. Hier kommen unterschiedliche Aromen und Strukturen zu einem ganz besonderen Geschmackserlebnis zusammen. Die zimtigen Süßkartoffeln bilden einen schönen Kontrast zum gebackenen Fenchel, der leichten, luftigen Quinoa und den knackigen Haselnüssen. Ihr könnt den Salat auch ganz einfach für unterwegs vorbereiten.","en-US":"This is a great mid week lunch salad, it’s filling and easy to take on-the-go with you. There is something pretty special about the combination of flavours and textures here. The soft, sweet nature of the cinnamon infused sweet potatoes contrasts perfectly with the roasted fennel, light fluffy quinoa and the crunchy hazelnuts.","en-US-POSIX":"This is a great mid week lunch salad, it’s lovely and filling and really easy to take on-the-go with you. There is something pretty special about the combination of flavors and textures here. The soft, sweet nature of the cinnamon-infused sweet potatoes contrasts perfectly with the roasted fennel, light fluffy quinoa and the crunchy hazelnuts."},"heroImage":{"en-US":{"metadata":{"tags":[]},"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"8ffyq0lxv9d2"}},"id":"78M3nyLykmn8rVZaVwVqth","type":"Asset","createdAt":"2019-01-18T14:13:01.379Z","updatedAt":"2021-06-08T09:53:03.059Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"master","type":"Link","linkType":"Environment"}},"revision":2},"fields":{"title":{"en-US":"RoastedSweetPotatoFennelHazlenutSalad "},"file":{"en-US":{"url":"//images.ctfassets.net/8ffyq0lxv9d2/78M3nyLykmn8rVZaVwVqth/a0bd89d0262cbf5b354abbadc91b3041/RoastedSweetPotatoFennelHazlenutSalad.jpg","details":{"size":2834294,"image":{"width":3294,"height":3294}},"fileName":"RoastedSweetPotatoFennelHazlenutSalad.jpg","contentType":"image/jpeg"}}},"id":"78M3nyLykmn8rVZaVwVqth"}},"images":{"en-US":[{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Asset","id":"5Jn7RZuLkhauG8IYxTqmRs"}}]},"servesMinimum":{"en-US":2},"servesMaximum":{"en-US":2},"prepTimeText":{"de":"60 Minuten","en-US":"60 minutes"},"cookTimeText":{"de":"40 Minuten","en-US":"40 minutes"},"totalMinutes":{"en-US":55},"ingredientSections":{"en-US":[{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"4unnO5bgvP2lA1UUaOulWJ"}}]},"method":{"en-US":[{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"01LZ8AmjvFM2rPDG0aTNvL"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"64EXpLniSn9MC0cHGZy03G"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"5bUMKEulQADsQYKcKhjxOe"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"3BeU7GBbUFvtQxvU7Y3K8x"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"5u4xK4XtWhUyqfLx8w8MIM"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"64nTbgaDFtoSCczuFjOweg"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"5Hh4Ia7pPMWSCedbqgEQjP"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"1HJXiR2EVoaGD6xTyLFopu"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"2ffJ1CU5uzu3ZlvY86fmOe"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"606b6oeYYrt1fFeyhM87BQ"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"5Sb6VLlzlFAHOLEJVl1Uqn"}}]},"relatedRecipes":{"en-US":[{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"1YWkpTTfokRopoBaCp5iML"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"1z7DJyxNOoygea22UQeewa"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"4bGRQSMaIc5pm8kT8SUo2A"}}]},"subcategories":{"en-US":[{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"1lP0PIf0m3xvIQb3OoRT1K"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"7Isz1ljJRHG1BySoPQ9uWr"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"5EPrj8oSzxJpVFNcpZrdPd"}}]},"freezable":{"en-US":false}},"contentType":"recipe","isAvailable":true,"new":false,"id":"2cqdoKM4RuCAsEHF0TAKoA","contentfulType":"recipe","visibility":"Public","presenter":{},"terms":{"en-US":"roasted sweet potato fennel hazelnut salad","de":"susskartoffel fenchel salat mit haselnussen"},"languages":["de","en-US","en-US-POSIX"],"pillars":[],"isSleep":false,"isWater":false,"categories":["2nNyXpAp40mosMAoI6iaiK"],"recipeCategories":[{"id":"2nNyXpAp40mosMAoI6iaiK","name":"Mains"}],"relatedTerms":{"en-US":"             quinoa  olive oil  sweet potato potatoes  raisins  blanched hazelnuts  dried rosemary  large fennel fennels  onion onions  lemon lemons  parsley  ground cinnamon  sea salt black pepper ","de":""},"isPlantBased":false,"allergyIDs":["6ZMKWrKQhUpBOHASExzcQK"],"allergies":["Nut"]},"14":{"metadata":{"tags":[],"concepts":[]},"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"8ffyq0lxv9d2"}},"id":"5UriKjGz0kcY6maqekiIKW","type":"Entry","createdAt":"2018-12-21T10:20:49.899Z","updatedAt":"2025-01-20T15:28:09.678Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"master","type":"Link","linkType":"Environment"}},"publishedVersion":187,"revision":24,"contentType":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"ContentType","id":"recipe"}}},"fields":{"title":{"de":"Süßkartoffel-Ecken aus dem Ofen","en-US":"Roasted Sweet Potato Wedges"},"slug":{"en-US":"roasted-sweet-potato-wedges"},"metaDescription":{"en-US":"I make these roasted sweet potato wedges a few times a week and I adore them. I love how the cinnamon and paprika absorb into the wedges as they bake so each bite is full of flavour. They’re amazing served hot straight out the oven."},"availableFrom":{"en-US":"2018-12-04T00:00"},"featuredFrom":{"en-US":"2021-03-30T00:00"},"featuredTo":{"en-US":"2021-03-31T00:00"},"featuredOrder":{"en-US":1},"categories":{"en-US":[{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"6E04w6vzcQwcswKIsIKeEI"}}]},"description":{"de":"Ich mache die Wedges ein paar Mal in der Woche, ich kann einfach nicht genug davon bekommen. Beim Backen nehmen sie den Geschmack des Zimts und der Paprika auf und jeder Bissen steckt voller Geschmack. Sie schmecken toll direkt aus dem Ofen – entweder als Teil einer großen Tafel oder mit Avocadocreme oder Hummus als einfaches Abendessen zu einem guten Film. Macht auf jeden Fall eine große Portion. Die Reste passen zu jeder schnellen Mahlzeit unter der Woche und sind toll als Basis fürs Mittagessen im Büro.","en-US":"I make these a few times a week and I adore them. I love how the cinnamon and paprika absorb into the wedges as they bake so each bite is full of flavour. They’re amazing served hot straight out the oven, either as part of a big spread or simply to eat with avocado cream or hummus for a simple movie night dinner for one! Make sure to cook extra though, the leftovers make the perfect addition to speedy meals throughout the week and a great base for work lunches.  ","en-US-POSIX":"I make these a few times a week and I adore them. I love how the cinnamon and paprika absorb into the wedges as they bake so each bit is full of flavor. They’re amazing served hot straight out of the oven, either as part of a big spread or simply to eat with avocado cream or hummus for a simple movie night dinner for one! Make sure to cook extra though, the leftovers make the perfect addition to speedy meals throughout the week and a great base for work lunches. "},"heroImage":{"en-US":{"metadata":{"tags":[]},"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"8ffyq0lxv9d2"}},"id":"2GgObbt55Kx0szo3oNpFOj","type":"Asset","createdAt":"2019-02-22T16:58:36.791Z","updatedAt":"2019-02-22T16:58:36.791Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"master","type":"Link","linkType":"Environment"}},"revision":1},"fields":{"title":{"en-US":"sweet potato wedges"},"file":{"en-US":{"url":"//images.ctfassets.net/8ffyq0lxv9d2/2GgObbt55Kx0szo3oNpFOj/4becd007f5158f8688147442e45e0fab/18-02-12-SweetPotatoWedges-9.jpg","details":{"size":5200196,"image":{"width":3598,"height":3598}},"fileName":"18-02-12-SweetPotatoWedges-9.jpg","contentType":"image/jpeg"}}},"id":"2GgObbt55Kx0szo3oNpFOj"}},"servesMaximum":{"en-US":2},"servesAlternateText":{"en-US":"2"},"totalMinutes":{"en-US":50},"ingredientSections":{"en-US":[{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"5mli5FhxewCkuY8gI2oQ8w"}}]},"method":{"en-US":[{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"3aVg9qpLOwyeKGssWqGY2o"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"33sNLX6EKkG4SQ8kck6iWk"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"6KEUGw7UT6WcWWeOIsiWQ2"}}]},"tip":{"de":"Diese Süßkartoffelecken schmecken köstlich mit Tahini oder Avocadocreme","en-US":"These sweet potato wedges are delicious served with tahini or avocado cream."},"relatedRecipes":{"en-US":[{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"4GqHcmwPsQmUeQiCyiUU4I"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"3KXjUb670sKiqEIEIkGmSq"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"7u5Q5tCkYHqs9f6NyegLUt"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"5rxFcbjLHyUIu2SCaEya0Q"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"2X1nk491qnevCBScV29pE2"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"7pEL0u2bodUkIR7gDcvOvS"}}]},"subcategories":{"en-US":[{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"4WXr60OwiXivSGX99s9O16"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"2I2ItwDXUGl9AW1hy0fVVu"}}]},"nutrients":{"en-US":["1 of your 5 a day"]}},"contentType":"recipe","isAvailable":true,"new":false,"id":"5UriKjGz0kcY6maqekiIKW","contentfulType":"recipe","visibility":"Public","featured":false,"featuredOrder":1,"presenter":{},"terms":{"en-US":"roasted sweet potato wedges","de":"susskartoffel ecken aus dem ofen"},"languages":["de","en-US","en-US-POSIX"],"pillars":[],"isSleep":false,"isWater":false,"categories":["6E04w6vzcQwcswKIsIKeEI"],"recipeCategories":[{"id":"6E04w6vzcQwcswKIsIKeEI","name":"Sides"}],"relatedTerms":{"en-US":"      olive oil  ground cinnamon  paprika  sea salt  sweet potato potatoes ","de":""},"isPlantBased":false,"allergyIDs":[],"allergies":[]},"15":{"metadata":{"tags":[],"concepts":[]},"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"8ffyq0lxv9d2"}},"id":"60qBlNJI6k8oYaAY8QG2kM","type":"Entry","createdAt":"2019-01-10T15:46:01.379Z","updatedAt":"2025-01-14T16:18:24.066Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"master","type":"Link","linkType":"Environment"}},"publishedVersion":225,"revision":12,"contentType":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"ContentType","id":"recipe"}}},"fields":{"title":{"de":"Gebackener Spargelbrokkoli","en-US":"Roasted Tenderstem","en-US-POSIX":"roasted broccolini"},"slug":{"en-US":"roasted-tenderstem"},"metaDescription":{"en-US":"I love roasted tenderstem broccoli, rather than boiled one. It creates an amazing, almost-charred crispy texture, which tastes delicious sprinkled with flakes of sea salt. We serve alongside our sweet potato and black bean shepherd's pie. "},"availableFrom":{"en-US":"2019-01-10T00:00"},"featuredFrom":{"en-US":"2022-02-13T00:00"},"featuredTo":{"en-US":"2022-02-14T00:00"},"categories":{"en-US":[{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"6E04w6vzcQwcswKIsIKeEI"}}]},"description":{"de":"Ich mag Spargelbrokkoli viel lieber gebacken als gekocht. Im Ofen wird er leicht gebräunt und wunderbar knusprig. Mit Meersalzflocken bestreut schmeckt er wirklich köstlich. Wir servieren ihn zu unserem Shepherd's Pie mit Süßkartoffeln und schwarzen Bohnen.  ","en-US":"I love to roast tenderstem broccoli, rather than boil it. It creates an amazing, almost-charred crispy texture, which tastes delicious sprinkled with flakes of sea salt. We serve alongside our sweet potato and black bean shepherd's pie. ","en-US-POSIX":"I love to roast broccolini, rather than boil it. It creates an amazing, almost-charred, crispy texture, which tastes delicious sprinkled with flakes of kosher salt. We serve alongside our sweet potato and black bean shepherd’s pie."},"heroImage":{"en-US":{"metadata":{"tags":[]},"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"8ffyq0lxv9d2"}},"id":"6bBxxeT22AmQUMoeUIG6O0","type":"Asset","createdAt":"2019-01-10T15:42:46.279Z","updatedAt":"2019-01-10T15:42:46.279Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"master","type":"Link","linkType":"Environment"}},"revision":1},"fields":{"title":{"en-US":"Roasted Tenderstem "},"file":{"en-US":{"url":"//im